This is the 1st version of API.
Contains 4 files -
onilne_food_ordering.py - the api
tests.py - unit tests for the api
models.py - the database
API Documentation - The documentation for the API

Technologies -
1) Python 3.6.4
2) Flask 0.12.2
3) sqlalchemy 1.2.2

Getting the API to work-
Install python3
Install flask using command - pip3 install Flask
Install SQLalchemy using command - pip3 install SQLalchemy
run the file online_food_ordering.py - python3 online_food_ordering.py
The server should be up and running on the port specified i.e 5000
In another terminal run the file tests.py - python3 tests.py
All tests should pass!
You can test out the API with your own custom input by using POSTMAN.
